import { useContext } from 'react'; import { contextApp } from '../context/ContextApp'; function TableOfPlanets() { // capturando as info da API lá do nosso arquivo responsável // por estabelecer o context API da aplicação. // Aquele arquivo irá 'prover' os outro com os dado da API const { planetData } = useContext(contextApp); return ( { planetData.map((planet) => ( ))}
Name Rotation Period Orbital Period Diameter Climate Gravity Terrain Surface Water Population Films Created Edited Url
{planet.name} {planet.rotation_period} {planet.orbital_period} {planet.diameter} {planet.climate} {planet.gravity} {planet.terrain} {planet.surface_water} {planet.population} {planet.filmes.map((mov) => mov)} {planet.created} {planet.edited} {planet.url}
); } export default TableOfPlanets;
